.iap2

  %h2 The proposition for deliberation

  %h3 "Meaningful" participation requires the satisfaction of (at least) the following criteria

  %ul
    %li Universal access
    %li Dialogue and deliberation
    %li Influence
    %li Acceptable Consensus

  %p Considering this:

  %h4 What could we do differently to institutionalise the above criteria?

  %h4 What could we do differently to scale up to address complexity?

  %h4 What could we do differently to scale out to involve many people?

